::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
NSF_abstract_words <- df |>
  filter(agency == "NSF") |>
  select(abstract) |>
  tidytext::unnest_tokens(word, abstract) |>
  count(word) |>
  anti_join(stop_words, by = "word")
```
